Okay, so this creates a kind of web linking all these artists together through the shows and movies they write music for. 
If we include Source 3's singles, we'll add another layer to the complexity. 
If we include all albums we want to keep track of, we'll add thousands of albums, sources and artists! Some sources even have 100+ albums to them (I'm looking at you, touhou).
This creates a giant web of connections and can't simply be displayed in a spreadsheet (you should see the spreadsheet I had before I decided to create this website!)<br><br>

So now enters this website. I wanted a way to keep track of all of albums that came out, along with the artist and source it belongs to. 
I also wanted to faciliate adding data and improving my visualizations of the connections.
Please explore the artists, albums, and sources pages and indices to get a better idea of how this plays out.
